high_descs: Turn right at the two open white doors and stop in front of the cell phone on the white shelf in front of you.
Pick up the cell phone on the right side of the white shelf.
Turn around and face the side of the gray chair with the open box on it.
Place the cell phone inside of the box on the gray chair.
Pick up the open box with the cell phone in it.
Turn around and walk to the black table on the right with the white vase on it.
Place the box down on the black table to the right of the white vase.
anns.task_desc: To move a box with a cell phone in it to the black table.

high_descs: Move to the shelf to the right of the black desk
Pick up a phone from the shelf
Move to the arm chair to the right of you
Put the phone in the box on the chair
Pick up the box from the chair
Move to the desk to the left of you
Put the box on the desk
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a phone on the black desk.

high_descs: Walk forwards and then turn right until you reach a white shelf
Pick up a cell phone from the white shelf
Turn around and then turn left. Turn to face your left so you are on the left side of the chair
Drop the cell phone into the cardboard box
Pick up the cardboard box off of the chair
Turn around and then face your right
Drop the cardboard box on to the black desk
anns.task_desc: Put a box containing a cell phone onto the black desk
